long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_GB,es,e:
Description
Warning! Virus is coming. Destroy them with your fingertip! Virus will be stronger each level, and you need to upgrade your ship and weapons.
Virus War - Anti Virus is a free casual shooting game. Using only your fingertips, kill all viruses. Remember to dodge, don't let those dirty things hit your ship!
Attractive game with more than 200 levels. let's show off!

*The gameplay is simple and attractive. Play Virus War anytime, anywhere; Enjoy maximum fun during your break!
*Equip your ships with different weapons to blow up hordes of enemies!
*Pass your friends on the leaderboard; Set a new record!

Instructions
Use the mouse pointer to play the game. Left click and move your spaceship.

*Note: We have added many external game links, making it easy for players to quickly access the games on our website https://monkeymart.org
